# Phase 4 — Dealer / Fleet Dealer / Admin profile architecture

## Objective

Add structured account types and permissions before integrating Meta.

## Roles

### 1. Super Admin

Platform-level control.
Can:

* manage all users
* manage all listings
* override listing state
* view all dealer Meta connections
* troubleshoot sync and permissions

### 2. Dealer

Single dealer account.
Can:

* manage own listings
* manage own staff
* connect own Meta Business assets
* manage own ad settings and feed settings
* view own leads

### 3. Pro Dealer

Multi-location or group dealer account.
Can:

* manage multiple dealer locations or branches
* manage branch inventory
* connect one or more Meta assets depending on business model
* assign staff by branch
* view roll-up reports

### 4. Owner-Operator

Individuals selling their machines.
Can:

* post one machine, or select multiple subscriptions in stripe
* manage their inventory
* receive leads
* 

### 4. Dealer Staff

Restricted user under dealer or fleet dealer.
Can:

* create/edit listings
* view assigned leads
* cannot change billing or top-level Meta asset connection unless allowed

